<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The former tech entrepreneur, =E2=80=9CRazzlek=
han=E2=80=9D rapper and accused cryptocurrency thief Heather Morgan has a n=
ew job.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Morgan, who dubbed herself on social media and=
 in music videos as =E2=80=9CThe Crocodile of Wall Street,=E2=80=9D was hir=
ed by an unspecified technology company even though she=E2=80=99s under 24-=
hour house arrest, according to a court filing. She and her husband are acc=
used of trying to launder $4.5 billion of Bitcoin stolen from the Bitfinex =
currency exchange.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">She asked a judge to modify the terms of her h=
ome confinement so she can work three days a week from the employer=E2=80=
=99s New York office. The government doesn=E2=80=99t object to the proposed=
 modification, her lawyer, Eugene Gorokhov, said in the filing Tuesday in W=
ashington.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Morgan, who has denied wrongdoing, was offered=
 a job =E2=80=9Cin the role of growth marketing and business development sp=
ecialist,=E2=80=9D Gorokhov said in the filing. He told the court that she=
=E2=80=99s seeking to keep the name of the employer secret to protect her s=
afety, though the government is aware of the identity.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I have to say that she is probably the only bu=
siness rapper whose stage name I know? And, no offense, not because she is =
so great at rapping? But because <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusi=
ness.com/click/30277130.281516/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9u=
L2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDItMDkvYnVzaW5lc3MtcmFwcGVyLXdhcy1iYWQtYXQtYml0Y29pbi1=
sYXVuZGVyaW5nP2NtcGlkPUJCRDAxMTcyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdX=
RtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMDExNyZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzd=
HVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB3210d5c4" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=
=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: =
none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; bo=
rder-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  getting arrested for a=
 multibillion-dollar Bitcoin heist</a> brings a lot of publicity to your bu=
siness rapping career? Like, that=E2=80=99s a growth marketing success righ=
t there, sure.</p>
